---
import CollectionLayout from '../../layouts/CollectionLayout.astro';
import { fetchProducts, getCategoryProducts } from '../../data/products';

const allProducts = await fetchProducts();
const products = getCategoryProducts(allProducts, 'ring-sets');
---

<CollectionLayout
  title="Meteorite Ring Sets"
  metaTitle="Meteorite Wedding Ring Sets | Jewelry by Johan"
  description="Matching meteorite wedding ring sets — engagement ring and wedding band combinations featuring authentic Gibeon meteorite, dinosaur bone, gold, and titanium. Handmade in USA."
  heading="Meteorite Ring Sets"
  subheading="Matching sets designed to be worn together — an engagement ring and wedding band united by the same cosmic materials, made by hand in Minneapolis."
  products={products}
  category="Ring Sets Collection"
>
  <section slot="editorial" class="collection-editorial">
    <div class="editorial-inner">
      <div class="editorial-divider"></div>
      <div class="editorial-grid">
        <div>
          <p>A meteorite ring set means both partners carry a fragment of the same ancient cosmos — matched in material, coordinated in design, made by the same skilled team in the same Minneapolis workshop. Each set is designed so the engagement ring and wedding band either nest flush together or complement each other's proportions when worn side by side.</p>
          <p>Most sets pair a wider men's band — typically 8mm or 10mm — with a narrower women's band or engagement ring. The meteorite inlays are cut from coordinating sections of authentic Gibeon iron so the crystal patterns feel visually related even as every fragment remains unique. Many sets incorporate additional materials: dinosaur bone, 14k yellow or rose gold, whiskey barrel oak, or diamond accents alongside the meteorite.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>Because every piece is made to order, width, metal, finish, and engraving can all be customized at checkout on <a href="https://jewelrybyjohan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jewelry by Johan</a>. <strong>Ring sets cannot be resized after production</strong> — use the <a href="/sizing-guide">sizing guide</a> carefully, or order <a href="https://jewelrybyjohan.com/products/ring-sizer-custom-made-1170" target="_blank" rel="noopener">custom ring sizers in both widths</a> before committing to production.</p>
          <p>Free laser engraving of up to 25 characters — with your choice of font — is included on each ring in the set. A matching set from this collection is one of the most personal ways two people can share the same piece of the solar system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</CollectionLayout>